{"text": "Asimismo el Gobierno rumano oñandukakuri ko'ára ta'ãnguéra legislativas ojoko fortalecer control tuguakuéra mutuos ári de inversiones jejaporã ndive de impedir pokarẽ, ñuhã ha momarandu añetegua'ỹ.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9986695051193237, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 25, "num_words_punct_spacy": 27, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 25, "num_chars": 197, "toxic_term_counts": {"pokarẽ": 1}}
{"text": "Dos últimos jasykuéra okára políticagui oime ñeĩ marcados por ñe'ẽ'apikuéra tee, principalmente entre Labastida ha Fox, quienes se oime ñe'enga desde mariquita, kelembu, tavyrai , mbyaipyre , yvy'akuéra fritas , producto chatarra ha karape , entre otros herokuéra.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9977028369903564, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 38, "num_words_punct_spacy": 43, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 34, "num_chars": 264, "toxic_term_counts": {"kelembu": 1, "tavyrai": 1}}
{"text": "Toledo omoma'ẽkuri que el Gobierno de Alberto Fujimori oguerekokuri kyhyje de participar en poravokuéra potĩ ha por ello ojapokuri un pokarẽ.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9992106556892395, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 21, "num_words_punct_spacy": 22, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 21, "num_chars": 141, "toxic_term_counts": {"pokarẽ": 1}}
{"text": "Toledo nomomaranduikuri al denunciar que atu'umi montaje ae de pokarẽ que, según omoma'ẽ, se orquestó icontrape ñembojere primerape celebrada el 9 de abril ojoko perpetuar a Fujimori katupe.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.984246015548706, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 28, "num_words_punct_spacy": 31, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 28, "num_chars": 190, "toxic_term_counts": {"pokarẽ": 1}}
{"text": "Toledo omoma'ẽkuri que porukái opotami llevarnos una pokarẽme ko poravope, oja'emi repetir pokarẽ ae ñekoni primeragua.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9945530891418457, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 16, "num_words_punct_spacy": 18, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 16, "num_chars": 119, "toxic_term_counts": {"pokarẽ": 1}}
{"text": "Ha duquesa, que de tavy sólo oguereko ahy'o, ombohováikuri: - Es que ahora noĩri genios.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9986987709999084, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 15, "num_words_punct_spacy": 19, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 14, "num_chars": 88, "toxic_term_counts": {"tavy": 1}}
{"text": "En los Estados Unidos se especula mucho teviro presunta ndive de Gere ha hasta oguata jehupyrekuéra tái que la confirmarían.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.881562352180481, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 20, "num_words_punct_spacy": 21, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 20, "num_chars": 124, "toxic_term_counts": {"teviro": 1}}
{"text": "Oha'e pituva cantar ko'ára jajái ha victoria del Barça.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9998644590377808, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 9, "num_words_punct_spacy": 10, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 9, "num_chars": 55, "toxic_term_counts": {"pituva": 1}}
{"text": "Sin embargo, sistema inmunológico avagua oha'e pituva de reconocer ko tesape'a pyahu.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9871070384979248, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 12, "num_words_punct_spacy": 14, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 12, "num_chars": 85, "toxic_term_counts": {"pituva": 1}}
{"text": "Quién, sino científico tavy películasgua de emba'ekuaa - ficción, oikatu haber diseñado una bacteria ha'u legionella, katupyry de sobrevivir un jerehape tan higiénico añemboapyte oha'e un ñongatuha de y potable ha de superar métodos tradicionales de ñemopotĩ?", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9973119497299194, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 37, "num_words_punct_spacy": 41, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 36, "num_chars": 259, "toxic_term_counts": {"tavy": 1}}
{"text": "Dentro novela teegui personajes suelen correrse poguasu juergas a rembe'y tekoasykuéragua de ZZNM, ha cierto rey ZZT, akaru si una rovetã guive de palacio viera un temimbo'epe riendo a pukasorokuéra con un apoi avatisokakuérape, comentó a sus kyta'i: Ese pyahu térã oĩ tavy térã omoñe'ẽ tembiasakuekuéra de ZZTO.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9994565844535828, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 48, "num_words_punct_spacy": 53, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 48, "num_chars": 312, "toxic_term_counts": {"tavy": 1}}
{"text": "Exteriorización mutua de lo a priori ha lo chae omomombyry aquí a Kant itemimo'ã añetetegua de que si hubiera de poner che ñeke'ãnguéra naturalespe determinación che tembipotagui vaihape, yo no me imputaría che actos mbóre koty'i que naha'ei apohára che naturalezagui sino que me la jecha dada.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9942785501480103, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 47, "num_words_punct_spacy": 49, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 47, "num_chars": 294, "toxic_term_counts": {"mbóre": 1}}
{"text": "La Policía sudafricana que patrulla zona ohi'ã pituva de detener rairõ.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.0, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": null, "language_identification_method": null, "num_words_split": 11, "num_words_punct_spacy": 12, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 11, "num_chars": 71, "toxic_term_counts": {"pituva": 1}}
{"text": "Intuición ka'avo los opehẽ'ãkuri en dos clases: chinos mbóre ha chinos marangatu.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9971591830253601, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 12, "num_words_punct_spacy": 14, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 12, "num_chars": 81, "toxic_term_counts": {"mbóre": 1}}
{"text": "Lo que ho'ytami Mae West de sí ae podríamos decirlo también karaikuéra: - Cuando roha'e katupyry roha'e muy marangatu, jepéramo cuando jaha'e mbóre roha'e porãve.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9996638298034668, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 25, "num_words_punct_spacy": 28, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 24, "num_chars": 162, "toxic_term_counts": {"mbóre": 1}}
{"text": "Lo vaive que okatu ser un yvypóra en España noha'ei oikotevẽva, ni tavyrai, ni pukarã, ni kelembu, sino desmazalado.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9872897863388062, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 19, "num_words_punct_spacy": 24, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 19, "num_chars": 116, "toxic_term_counts": {"kelembu": 1, "tavyrai": 1}}
{"text": "Cuando un výro oarapa ihova ojogua una expresión tan sugeridora de kuaaha akaru la genio kakuaagui.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9947474598884583, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 16, "num_words_punct_spacy": 17, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 16, "num_chars": 99, "toxic_term_counts": {"výro": 1}}
{"text": "Oha'emi igualitos a Leocadio, výro távagui.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9997086524963379, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 6, "num_words_punct_spacy": 8, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 6, "num_chars": 43, "toxic_term_counts": {"výro": 1}}
{"text": "Amo pukavy ritual, una jurukechẽ encausada ha gratuita, pukarã, noha'eimi más que un jerekoha tavy tee ojoko propiciar otros ñeha'uvõnguéra improbables favorables, una ñuhã burda tendida hacia sí ae cada pyharevekue, una tovatavy más.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9950258135795593, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 34, "num_words_punct_spacy": 40, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 34, "num_chars": 234, "toxic_term_counts": {"tavy": 1}}
{"text": "Un kuatia de la Policía Antinarcóticos difundido ko'ára diariore El Universo omoma'ẽ que mafias internacionales oime usado ko decisión omombyta blanquear pirapire térã introducir billetes pokarẽ, especialmente de Colombia.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9576947689056396, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 29, "num_words_punct_spacy": 31, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 29, "num_chars": 222, "toxic_term_counts": {"pokarẽ": 1}}
{"text": "Asu oĩ jehupyre una anana en torno a Jospin al tildar iñe'ẽnguekuéra de ñe'ẽ japu'ỹva, mientras que derecha oime denunciado una pituva pohýi, un fiasco, ‘a ñaña cohabitacióngua.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9971905946731567, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 28, "num_words_punct_spacy": 33, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 28, "num_chars": 177, "toxic_term_counts": {"pituva": 1}}
{"text": "Aparicio considera que oĩ que ser py'ahatã ha mbóre yvypóra ojoko meter chuchu a avakuéra que después muchos arajerekuéragui de jepytaso ha de sacrificio, sólo oguereko jepytaha ha ombojo'a oĩ quien por kuaahakuéra electorales oja'e jugar contra ellos.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9984656572341919, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 38, "num_words_punct_spacy": 40, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 38, "num_chars": 252, "toxic_term_counts": {"mbóre": 1}}
{"text": "Oguereko potencial opyta estar entre los primeros, jepéramo inicios oha'et difíciles, ajepy'ajoko lo oha'et también escuderíape Williams, que opapat otra fabricantendi que ojere a la Fórmula Uno, BMW, ha Prost, que a py'apy de tener motor Peugeot, oha'e pituva de hacer un coche competitivo.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9922254681587219, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 44, "num_words_punct_spacy": 52, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 44, "num_chars": 291, "toxic_term_counts": {"pituva": 1}}
{"text": "Aún apyhykuri, Joachim Bjorklund, quien destacó importancia de las dos kyta'i jornadas de liga - ya que el Deportivo debe recibir al Valencia ha viajar al Camp Nou - orovia que equipo gallego oha'et pituva de ganar ã dos ñembosaráikuéra.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.692963182926178, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 40, "num_words_punct_spacy": 43, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 38, "num_chars": 237, "toxic_term_counts": {"pituva": 1}}
{"text": "Lo logramos; nañambojáraikuri ni un pyrũ en pokarẽ, ni un jehasaha atrás, ho'ytakuri Marroquín ante mongoraha de 30 ijirũnguéragui que opytakuri sin ingerir tembi'ukuéra pasado guive Martes.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9988791346549988, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 27, "num_words_punct_spacy": 31, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 27, "num_chars": 190, "toxic_term_counts": {"pokarẽ": 1}}
{"text": "Mburuvicha de la SRB argumentó igualmente que jurupeteĩ de retención de embarques noha'ei kotevẽpyre debido a que repy de tesa ho'akuri ñemuha internacionalpe debido a que tetãnguéra importadores orekomi ñeimo'ã pokarẽ de que Brasil ohomi a producir 40 millones de sacas (de 60 kilos) remitỹnguepe que omboypy ko arajere.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9950294494628906, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 49, "num_words_punct_spacy": 52, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 49, "num_chars": 321, "toxic_term_counts": {"pokarẽ": 1}}
{"text": "Aimo'ã que después de esto positivo que oĩ ocurrido, ha a mbyasy del poco ára que queda opyta Sydney, ñembosako'i oho a ser porãve, noha'ei que haya sido mbóre, jepéramo a partir de ahora oho a ser porãve, oha'uvõkuri.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.999444305896759, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 39, "num_words_punct_spacy": 45, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 39, "num_chars": 218, "toxic_term_counts": {"mbóre": 1}}
{"text": "Ñembohovái oĩ iniciado una ñepu'ã histórica contra pokarẽ con concentraciones ko'ẽregua plazaspe de Belgrado ha otras ciudades serbias ha pytu'u ndive de escuelas, universidades, ñemomýi, fábricas ha tekoha'angakuéra.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9996371269226074, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 28, "num_words_punct_spacy": 32, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 28, "num_chars": 217, "toxic_term_counts": {"pokarẽ": 1}}
{"text": "Ñembohovakekuéra se omoheñóikuri cuando una teta que ombohováimi pokarẽ electoralre oguahẽmbakuri en el céntrico Parlamento federal yugoslavo al añepyrũ una mbohovái grangui ñembohováigui.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9983404278755188, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 23, "num_words_punct_spacy": 24, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 23, "num_chars": 188, "toxic_term_counts": {"pokarẽ": 1}}
{"text": "Hpego aporeko legalpe lo oime demostrado ko crisispe, en la que ñe'ẽrendu'ỹ civil oha'ekuri jave apelaciónndi a todas instancias judiciales ojoko que reconocieran pokarẽ electoral, ma'ẽra que ombopahakuri de hacer ko'ára el Tribunal Constitucional.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9956276416778564, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 34, "num_words_punct_spacy": 37, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 34, "num_chars": 248, "toxic_term_counts": {"pokarẽ": 1}}
{"text": "Extranjero tavy oha'e un filme vitalista que ombovy'a acontecer cotidiano una comunidad kytomigua zíngara en Rumanía ha oho acompañada una banda sugerentegua ipúva con músicas ko colectivogui.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9963992834091187, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 27, "num_words_punct_spacy": 28, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 27, "num_chars": 192, "toxic_term_counts": {"tavy": 1}}
{"text": "Kuarahysẽ, a instancias algunos pohanohárakuéragua, oñepyrũ a dictar pituva jurídica de algunas afectadasgui térã a ordenar directamente ijeike en puru'ãnguéra sanitarios que puedan controlar iñemongaru.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9958202838897705, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 25, "num_words_punct_spacy": 28, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 25, "num_chars": 203, "toxic_term_counts": {"pituva": 1}}
{"text": "Sólo apýrape se vio tembo con el piercing.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.0, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": null, "language_identification_method": null, "num_words_split": 8, "num_words_punct_spacy": 9, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 8, "num_chars": 42, "toxic_term_counts": {"tembo": 1}}
{"text": "Si ijirũnguéra lo orohorymi ha'u tavy, guapyha no olvidaba ijyvypórape, mientras opoimi jurupytekuéra temirendupe.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9999368190765381, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 14, "num_words_punct_spacy": 17, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 14, "num_chars": 114, "toxic_term_counts": {"tavy": 1}}
