{"text": "Según otras ñeimo'ãnguéra, oime sido pituva de Occidente omombyta comprender lo que realmente oikovemi ha okatumi pasar en Rusia si se la dejaba ijyvytupe satisfaciendo kuaasekuéra élites tujugua poscomunistas, a jeva de eliminar un ára rehe a Moscú actividad internacionalgui.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.990677535533905, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 40, "num_words_punct_spacy": 43, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 40, "num_chars": 277, "toxic_term_counts": {"pituva": 1}}
{"text": "El Gobierno también avanzó que omba'apot con contundencia ojoko mejorar ñorairõ contrame pokarẽ fiscal.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.831882655620575, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 14, "num_words_punct_spacy": 15, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 14, "num_chars": 103, "toxic_term_counts": {"pokarẽ": 1}}
{"text": "Entre los que se oime vuelto tavy por Todo che sy ári ta'anga Sean Connery, con quien oñomongetakuri antes de recibir el Oscar.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.0, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": null, "language_identification_method": null, "num_words_split": 23, "num_words_punct_spacy": 25, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 23, "num_chars": 127, "toxic_term_counts": {"tavy": 1}}
{"text": "Pasajeros ojejokokuri con estoicismo ipo'a mbóre un ñoirũ de horas.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9921743869781494, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 10, "num_words_punct_spacy": 11, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 10, "num_chars": 67, "toxic_term_counts": {"mbóre": 1}}
{"text": "Más que clásicospe, ko escena nos omomandu'a un bolero de La Trinca tenói Corazón tavy, tembiasakue de dos tayhukuéra, Catalunhaa y España, republicanos ha conservadores, nacionalistas ha españolistas.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.96605384349823, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 28, "num_words_punct_spacy": 34, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 28, "num_chars": 201, "toxic_term_counts": {"tavy": 1}}
{"text": "Solventar problema pagando - - a cinco pesetas térã a cinco céntimos ta'ãha cúbico, ome'ẽ jojaha - - sentaría un precedente mbóre.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9892447590827942, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 22, "num_words_punct_spacy": 24, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 18, "num_chars": 130, "toxic_term_counts": {"mbóre": 1}}
{"text": "Martín oĩmi negado anteriormente tekove de pokarẽ alguno.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9073936343193054, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 8, "num_words_punct_spacy": 9, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 8, "num_chars": 57, "toxic_term_counts": {"pokarẽ": 1}}
{"text": "Todo kyre'ỹ ohi'ã un výro, teniendo en cuenta cómo evoluciona yvóra, omomarandukuri Harnoncourt.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9843065142631531, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 13, "num_words_punct_spacy": 16, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 13, "num_chars": 96, "toxic_term_counts": {"výro": 1}}
{"text": "Acusado de pokarẽ ha condenado a tres arajerekuéra ha mbytere de kuarahy'ã en 1997, Peter ohokuri koty'i en tekosã'ỹ primavera de 1998.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9977143406867981, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 22, "num_words_punct_spacy": 24, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 22, "num_chars": 135, "toxic_term_counts": {"pokarẽ": 1}}
{"text": "Los que no comulgan personaje ndive, jepéramo agradecieron intento de farsa costumbrista de Torrente, jyva tavy tembiapoukapygua, okuaa que se omboguapy decepcionados.", "corpus": "ancora", "corpus_file": "raw_ancora.tsv", "source": "unknown", "url": "unknown", "language": "grn", "language_score": 0.9912983179092407, "language_script": "Latn", "language_score_source": "glotlid", "language_identification_method": "agree_glotlib_fasttext_openlid", "num_words_split": 22, "num_words_punct_spacy": 26, "num_words_no_punct_spacy": 22, "num_chars": 167, "toxic_term_counts": {"tavy": 1}}
